    <title>hexo搭建博客图片无法显示问题</title>
    <link href="https://profond.github.io/2021/08/24/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/"/>
    <id>https://profond.github.io/2021/08/24/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/</id>
    <published>2021-08-24T03:22:52.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-08-24T03:34:26.118Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>1.安装插件npm install hexo-asset-image –save</p><p>2.修改主_config.yml配置</p><p><img src="/2021/08/24/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/01-16297758930222.png" alt="1"></p><p>3.修改hexo-asset-image(位于themes下)</p><p><img src="/2021/08/24/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E5%9B%BE%E7%89%87%E6%97%A0%E6%B3%95%E6%98%BE%E7%A4%BA%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98/2.png" alt="2"></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;1.安装插件npm install hexo-asset-image –save&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;2.修改主_config.yml配置&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;/2021/08/24/hexo%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%</summary>
      
    
    
    
    
